{"tid":1598526,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方 9 月中購入約 20 套 3M 防毒面具　與示威者使用款式相似","createTime":"2019-09-27T13:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:48:32.000Z","uid":68738,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc93ed04c6aff8c66e88648063f585f95606ad8","tid":1598526,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mask-22_PRSXH_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmask-22_PRSXH_1200x0.png&h=9433e41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反送中運動至今三個多月，警方多次派警員喬裝示威者作拘捕行動，引發爭議，網上亦經常有人指一些激進示威者是警員假扮的「鬼」，警方多次否認；《立場新聞》獲悉，警方在 9 月中曾以近萬元，購入約 20 個示威者常用的防毒面具的濾罐，防毒面具的 3M 的 7502，濾罐則是粉紅色的 3M 60926。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》向警方查詢，這批防毒面具和濾罐是否用於喬裝行動，警方在處理反送中的「踏浪者」行動中，合共購入多少民用防毒面具和濾罐，派出過多少次喬裝警員和人數，目前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n根據《立場》獲得的資料，警方這次採購合共是 20 套防毒面具，每個配備兩個濾罐，購入的防毒面具是直接交到灣仔警察總部，而批出相關採購的是助理署長（刑事）袁旭健。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-9-%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%BC%E5%85%A5%E7%B4%84-20-%E5%A5%97-3m-%E9%98%B2%E6%AF%92%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%B7-%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AC%BE%E5%BC%8F%E7%9B%B8%E4%BC%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9-9-%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25B4%2584-20-%25E5%25A5%2597-3m-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%25AF%2592%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%2585%25B7-%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BC%25BC%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHfLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=74fd6f1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9-9-%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25B4%2584-20-%25E5%25A5%2597-3m-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%25AF%2592%